                    </div>
                    <span>This book, as opposed to other books concerning "Temperament Typing" offers a less official, more relaxed and practical way of harnessing this theory.  I think it is worth a read for everyone who feels he wants or needs to know people more, on both the personal or impersonal level</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">EYE OPENER-BRILLIANT book!</div>
